item.dc:creator: @SGTCannon SGTCannon
item.description:
@SGTCannon wrote:

If that happens it means the models cannot work, on a 317 (im not sure if its delta based only), there is a limit to how many points and faces you can have on an object.

Now I know those staff capes work, so you may want to check your models in the class8 ints that you placed to make sure they match the model #'s that you placed. - I’m not sure about the t-shirt and other item

This should have been posted in client help
